NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
C.D., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
A.H., Defendant. In the Matter of the Guardianship of K.D., a Minor-Respondent. C-170 September Term 2017
078827 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 16, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001394-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
